---
import Layout from "../../layouts/layout.astro";

import "../../css/fundadores.css";
---

<Layout>
  <section id="inicio">
    <div class="content content-inicio">
      <div class="content-limit">
        <h1>FOUNDER<span>.</span></h1>
        <br />
        <br />
        <p class="p-inicio">
          David Adissi is founder and CEO of n.technology as well as a racing
          driver.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="content content-provi">
      <div class="content-limit">
        <div class="card-gray">
          <div class="flex justify-between align-center gap-3 mt-4">
            <div style="width: 50%;">
              <h2 class="font-5">
                Coming from this world most of his business experience and his
                first approaches with technology<span class="color-verde"
                  >.</span
                >
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div style="width: 50%;">
              <img
                src="/img/david-first.png"
                alt="David"
                style="width: 100%;"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between align-center gap-3 mt-1">
            <div style="width: 50%;">
              <img
                src="/img/david-second.png"
                alt="David"
                style="width: 100%;"
              />
            </div>
            <div style="width: 50%;">
              <p class="font-light">
                Central to Adissi's mission is a profound dedication to
                advancing industries through state-of-the-art technologies.
              </p>
              <p class="font-light">
                With visionary guidance, Adissi spearheads the creation of
                innovative solutions that propel industries into the digital
                age, fostering unmatched growth and efficiency.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3 mt-3">
            <div style="width: 50%;">
              <p class="font-light" style="font-size: 15px;">
                However, Adissi's vision goes beyond technological advancement;
                encompasses a deep understanding of the social implications of
                technology. Recognizing technology as a cornerstone of social
                sustainability and progress, Adissi strives to harness its
                potential to accelerate the evolution of society.
              </p>
              <p class="font-light" style="font-size: 15px;">
                Central to Adissi's beliefs is the principle of inclusion. He
                strongly believes in making technology accessible to everyone,
                regardless of technical skill or economic status. Emphasizing
                the importance of inclusivity, Adissi advocates for a paradigm
                shift toward a technological landscape that prioritizes equity
                over privilege.
              </p>
              <p class="font-light" style="font-size: 15px;">
                Fundamentally, Adissi's journey exemplifies the convergence of
                technological evolution, visionary leadership and social impact.
                As the founder Of a company dedicated to transforming industries
                and fostering beneficial change, Adissi remains unwavering in
                his dedication to propelling society forward through technology.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="img-compo-fundador">
              <img src="/img/auto-team.png" alt="" style="width: 100%;" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <img
            src="/img/car-fundador.png"
            alt=""
            style="width: 100%; margin-top: -100px;"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="content content-racing content-image">
      <div class="content-limit">
        <h2 class="text-center" style="font-size:70px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
          n<span class="color-verde">.</span>technology Racing
        </h2>
        <p class="color-verde text-center font-3 mt-1">
          <strong>Lamborghini Super Trofeo North America</strong>
        </p>

        <div class="flex align-center justify-center gap-4 mt-2">
          <div class="flex align-center" style="flex-direction: column;">
            <img src="/img/racing-david.png" style="width: 100%;" alt="David" />
            <span>David Adissi</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex align-center" style="flex-direction: column;">
            <img src="/img/racing-luis.png" style="width: 95%;" alt="Luis" />
            <span>Luis "Chapulín" Díaz</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="content content-car-video">
      <div class="content-limit relative" style="padding-bottom: 100px;">
        <video class="video-car" controls muted>
          <source src="/img/car.mp4" />
        </video>

        <img
          src="/img/circle-video-fondo.png"
          alt=""
          class="img-circle-fondo-video absolute"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
